1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,200
Light is both wave and particle — a photon is its mysterious packet.

2
00:00:05,200 --> 00:00:09,600
These tiny particles carry energy, zipping through space at incredible speeds.

3
00:00:09,600 --> 00:00:10,400
But wait.

4
00:00:10,400 --> 00:00:14,400
How can something be both a wave and a particle?

5
00:00:14,400 --> 00:00:16,000
It’s the wave-particle duality!

6
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:19,200
When we observe photons, they behave like particles.

7
00:00:19,200 --> 00:00:22,400
Yet, when unobserved, they display their wave nature.

8
00:00:22,400 --> 00:00:23,200
Mind-blowing, right?

9
00:00:23,200 --> 00:00:24,400
Curious for more?

10
00:00:24,400 --> 00:00:27,600
Follow for your daily dose of science magic!
